name: Kyle Norton
tweets: @toojoe @ThreatNotation It comes down to convention and readability. Quarter note is convenient as the beat since a sustained pitch can be represented as a half or whole note rather than multiple quarter notes tied together. With the whole note as the beat, you could only extend by tying them together.
